description: SoFa-Network (wormhole network) is an Internet underlying communication infrastructure which combines network communication protocol, block chain book and application layer SDK. SoFa-Network builds a dynamic multi-protocol MPN network (Multi-p2p-Network) through the self-developed Multi-p2pProtocol. It is proved by Proof of Packet packet transmission that the packet transmission exchange between network nodes is signed and accounted for. The value transfer between nodes in the network is quantitatively counted and settled by block chain. Based on MPN, a wealth of SDK, is provided to support the development and landing use of all kinds of applications based on SoFa-Network.
name: Phantom Matter
